{"tid":62191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沖天炮沒從屁股飛出　男子被跨年煙火爆菊","createTime":"2016-12-31T17:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T19:42:12.000Z","uid":19707,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8596a718228783c219000cfc43d7549af4633d82","tid":62191,"uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T17:20:59.000Z","msg":"男子被跨年煙火給爆菊了！<br />\n <br />\n臉書粉絲專頁「UNILAD」分享一段影片，男子脫下褲子後將沖天炮塞在屁股內固定，並且點火後準備讓沖天炮筆直往上沖，但是不知道是否因為太緊張讓屁股出太多力氣，或者是沖天炮的沖力不夠，導致沖天炮完全沒有飛出去的意思，直接在屁股引爆。<br />\n <br />\n網友看到這幕紛紛留言「超級狂」、「年度最佳愚蠢代表」、「菊花開花」、「我想知道他屁股裂開沒」、「愚蠢的白痴」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n片：<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170101/1025473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170101%2F1025473&d=ZYc2wPIhczhU5fd6Z4tmBJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=0071a918\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170101/1025473</a>"},{"pid":"91ebf99581806b51f0b9484545683e503bddc2a0","tid":62191,"uid":1701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T17:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec97e5e3e58dfbae3eee7f70acb31e7df658fe80","tid":62191,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:24:16.000Z","msg":"2017 第一個達爾文獎候選人"},{"pid":"a148b52a50b727ef1d3ec1a1a421a7d3dccd633d","tid":62191,"uid":26185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdd38e5eff9c9b1e9080d193d2b0894471aec5f","tid":62191,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:26:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35ee1478306d22ebc8ea067ef00cd7cc943633b1","tid":62191,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass